"ngram\": \"Data\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"80 percent\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"the Phryges\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quanzhou Nanyang Arts & Crafts Co., Ltd. is a commissioned manufacturer of the event's mascots.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Quanzhou Nanyang Arts\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"Crafts Co.\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"a commissioned manufacturer\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"the event's mascots\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Phryge is known for its unique standing posture, with its slender legs supporting a large body, making it a challenging design in the production process,\\\" said Jiang Lingyan, senior sales manager of the company.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Phryge\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"its unique standing posture\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"its slender legs\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"a large body\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the production process\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"Jiang Lingyan\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"senior sales manager\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The design team innovatively combined two types of polyvinyl chloride (PVC) material in one Phryge to address the potential bumps and impacts during international long-distance transport.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyvinyl_chloride\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"polyvinyl chloride\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyvinyl_chloride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyvinyl_chloride\"}], \"noun_phra